import React, { useState } from 'react';
import { Box, Grid, Typography, makeStyles, FormControl, InputLabel, OutlinedInput, Link, Button } from '@material-ui/core';

const useStyles = makeStyles(theme => ({
    root: { height: "100vh", width: "100vw" },
    loginFormContainer: { margin: "0 auto" }
}))

const Login = () => {
    const classes = useStyles();
    const [Email, setEmail] = useState("")

    return (
        <>
            <Box className={classes.root} py={15}>
                <Grid container>
                    <Grid item lg={4} md={8} xs={10} className={classes.loginFormContainer} >
                        <Box py={4} style={{ border: "1px solid lightgrey", borderRadius: "10px" }}>
                            <Box>
                                <Typography variant="h4" align="center" gutterBottom>Google</Typography>
                                <Typography variant="h5" align="center">Sign in</Typography>
                                <Typography variant="subtitle1" align="center">to continue to Gmail</Typography>
                            </Box>
                            <Box px={2} py={3}>
                                <form>
                                    <FormControl fullWidth variant="outlined">
                                        <InputLabel htmlFor="outlined-adornment-Email">Email or phone</InputLabel>
                                        <OutlinedInput id="outlined-adornment-Email" labelWidth={120} name="email" value={Email} onChange={(e) => setEmail(e.target.value)} />
                                    </FormControl>
                                    <Link href="#" style={{ fontWeight: "500" }}>Forgot email?</Link>
                                    <Box mt={5} style={{ display: 'flex', justifyContent: 'space-between', alignItems: "center" }}>
                                        <Link>Create account</Link>
                                        <Button type="submit" color="primary" variant="contained" >Next</Button>
                                    </Box>
                                </form>
                            </Box>
                        </Box>
                    </Grid>
                </Grid>
            </Box>
        </>
    )
}

export default Login
